1 13A.
2 (12) Any person who holds a license to practice as a registered nurse in this state shall
3 have the right to use the title "registered nurse" and the abbreviation "R.N." No
4 other person shall assume the title or use the abbreviation or any other words,
5 letters, signs, or figures to indicate that the person using the same is a registered
6 nurse. No person shall practice as a registered nurse unless licensed under this
