23 school nurse or other licensed health care practitioner is not immediately
24 available and the trained individual believes in good faith that a student is
25 experiencing severe hypoglycemia or other conditions noted in that
26 student's diabetes medical management plan, regardless of whether that
27 student has a prescription for glucagon.
